; Regression test for issue #745: ledger budget: Error: Cannot multiply an amount with a balance (BZ#745)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/745
; The budget report with multiple expense categories previously produced:
; "Error: Cannot multiply an amount with a balance"

~ Monthly
    Expenses:Food    $500
    Expenses:Rent    $1000
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $300
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/15 Rent Payment
    Expenses:Rent    $1000
    Assets:Checking

test --budget bal -e 2024/02/01
                $200  Assets:Checking
               $-200  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
